otices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-7Ee","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":2033,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/02\/wealth-of-the-spirit\/","url_meta":{"origin":29402,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Peace: True wealth is contentment of the soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWealth\u00a0is not in having many possessions. Rather, true wealth\u00a0is the richness of the soul.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6446, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1051 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5199,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/best-sadaqah-tazkiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":29402,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Best charity is most difficult to give","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which charity has the greatest reward?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat you give charity while you are healthy, greedy, fearing poverty, and hoping to be rich. Do not delay\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15546,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/05\/truly-poor-do-not-beg\/","url_meta":{"origin":29402,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Beggars: Truly poor people refrain from begging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe poor person is not the one who is satisfied with a date or two, or a morsel or two, but rather the poor person is only one who abstains from begging. Recite the verse if\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15544,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/05\/punishment-akhirah-begging\/","url_meta":{"origin":29402,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Beggars: Punishment for too much begging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man continues to beg people until he will come on the Day of Resurrection without any flesh on his face.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1474, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1040 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15548,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/05\/charity-upper-hand-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":29402,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Giving charity is better than receiving it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe upper hand is better than the lower hand.\u00a0The upper hand is one that gives and the lower hand is one that takes.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1429, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1033 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5831,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/02\/independence-better-begging\/","url_meta":{"origin":29402,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Work: Earning yourself better than begging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, if one of you were to carry a bundle of firewood on his back and sell it, that would be better for him than begging a man\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.